        "id": "claim.repo_identity",
        "kind": "fact",
        "text": "Gemini Voyager is a browser extension that enhances Google Gemini with timeline navigation, two-level folder organization, a prompt vault, Google Drive cloud sync, chat export, formula copy, Mermaid rendering, Deep Research extraction, and several sidebar/input behavior tools.",
